description: Try our easy to follow Filo Fish Pies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Filo Fish Pies Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400 g barramundi fillets with lemon & parsley butter

recipeInstructions.text: On the same tray, place sweet potato wedges, lightly spray with oil and sprinkle with sesame seeds. Bake for 20 minutes or until sweet potato is cooked and pies are lightly golden. Serve fish pies with a salad of spinach and cherry tomatoes and sweet potato fries.
